{
  "stem": "6900.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there was one of our girls, she was a shirt maker.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So she used to-- they used-- one-- an old soldier, not an SS, an old soldier used to pick her up and take her to where the SS.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She used to have to make shirts for them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So when we get to the bahnhof where the trucks were, she spoke to him.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And she said our group would like to stay.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "All right?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We'd like to stay, she said, together.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So he said, well, wait till the end.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He said, and what's more, there's going to be straw on the floor.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Anyway, that's what happened.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We waited till the end, and we were in this truck where there was straw on the floor.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] we get to Den-- to Padborg.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "That's the first crossing in Denmark.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The SS were with us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They opened the doors, and then we saw Danish people throwing parcels over the big wire fence.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So the SS went and picked them out-- up, because they didn't have any food, either.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They went and picked them up, and they were gone.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The SS were gone.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They shut the trucks again, and [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] we were off.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "When they stopped eventually, we were in Copenhagen.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there was all Red Cross on the station with food.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But we couldn't stomach it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We couldn't.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Then from there, they put us in coaches and sent us to a cleansing station.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They took what we had on off.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They-- they shaved our heads.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They gave us a clean towel and a piece of soap.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "There were doctors and nurses there and showers.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And that was the best present I'd had in my life-- a clean towel and a piece of soap.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
